HEADWORD: Logotype
<hw>Log"o*type</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>lo`gos</grk> word + <ets>-type</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Print.)</fld>
<def>A single type, containing two or more letters; <as>as,
<ex>⟦ae⟧</ex>, <ex>\⟦oe⟧</ex>, <ex>⟦AE⟧</ex>, <ex>⟦filig⟧</ex>,
<ex>⟦fllig⟧</ex>, <ex>⟦ffllig⟧</ex>, etc.</as>; -- called also
<altname>ligature</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

